NK020(wa)007:0: rang rang so so'i sngags mthar nam mkha' mdzod kyi
NK020(wa)007:1: sham bu btags la thams cad la lan gsum gsum
NK020(wa)007:3: dngos grub blang ba'i las rim zur bkol nyer bsdus ni /
NK020(wa)007:4: a kra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum ka ta ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)007:5: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum
NK020(wa)007:6: sarba ta th+aa ga ta kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum
NK020(wa)007:7: / badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK020(wa)007:8: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK020(wa)007:13: rak+sha sh+ri he ru ka rak+ta kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK020(wa)007:35: badz+ra +aar+ya te dza te nga dzah a mu khe h+aum /
NK020(wa)007:37: b+hasmi pa la ya ba tu hoh badz+ra a pra
NK020(wa)007:38: ti ha ta +aar+ya ni tsa tu ra ta ra
NK020(wa)007:39: phata rak+mo h+aum / sh+r+ai badz+ra mung+ga ra mu kha shwa ra y+aa ya na ma /
NK020(wa)007:41: ra ga ma shwa ra y+aa ya /
NK020(wa)007:42: kha t+w+aam ka pra dz+wa la y+aa ya /
NK020(wa)007:43: g+han+de pra dz+wa la y+aa ya /
NK020(wa)007:62: ma h+aa m+aa ra n+aa badz+ra /
NK020(wa)007:75: kid+ga ra ha ha ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK020(wa)007:77: b+ha na b+ha na ang+ku sha dzah ha la ha la p+aa sha h+aum /
NK020(wa)007:79: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+de hoh ma me shwa ra h+aum /
NK020(wa)007:80: ma h+aa gu ru sha ri ram g+ai li h+aum /
NK020(wa)007:81: badz+ra yo gi gu ru sa ma ya dzahbadz+ra am
NK020(wa)007:82: ku sha dzah ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum
NK020(wa)007:83: / dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs 'khor dang bcas pa
NK020(wa)007:84: 'od dang sprul par bcas te gsal shing gyi rtse
NK020(wa)007:86: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta /
NK020(wa)007:88: ma h+aa rak+ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK020(wa)007:90: dkyil 'khor lha tshogs thugs ka nas //
NK020(wa)007:91: zur brgyad dkyil nas 'bru brgyad shar //
NK020(wa)007:92: snying po ru lu 'bru brgyad dang //
NK020(wa)007:94: phar 'phros lha tshogs thug dam bskang //
NK020(wa)007:95: tshur 'dus bdag la dngos grub stsol //
NK020(wa)007:96: rang sngags la ru lu sbrel ba dang /
NK020(wa)007:97: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na bo d+hi tsit+ti ma h+aa su kha h+aum h+aum /
NK020(wa)007:99: brjod med shes rab sogs kyis bstod /
NK020(wa)007:102: gsol byang gi smon lam ni /
NK020(wa)007:103: hoh bcom ldan 'das dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs yab
NK020(wa)007:104: yum sprul pa phyag brnyan dang bcas pa la dngos
NK020(wa)007:105: grub tu gsol ba'i mdo ni /
NK020(wa)007:106: bdag cag gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir tshogs pa rnams la /
NK020(wa)007:107: shes bya thams cad la thogs pa med pa'i shes rab /
NK020(wa)007:113: bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po'i sku gsung thugs kyi
NK020(wa)007:114: bla man chad nas dngos grub kyi skal ba dang
NK020(wa)007:115: rigs rgyud gang lags pa thams cad phyi mar sdad
NK020(wa)007:116: mi 'tshal bar dus da lta nyid du thob par
NK020(wa)007:119: badz+ra ang+ku sha dzah zhes lan gsum gyis /
NK020(wa)007:122: gsum pas sku 'od du zhu nas rang la thim
NK020(wa)007:123: pas sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las kyi gzi
